fr:mainmatter.fr:p:
Given a diagram D, the cocone functor C\xrightarrow {\operatorname *{Cocone}_F}
Set is the functor C\xrightarrow {\Delta }C^J\xrightarrow {\operatorname {Hom}(F, -)}\operatorname {Set}, where \Delta  embeds objects
as the appropriate constant functors.

